Package: AHBPCEPredR
Type: Package
Title: Cardiopulmonary Exercise Testing and Pulmonary Function Predictions
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Tom", "Alexander", email = "thomas.alexander3@va.gov", 
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Shobhik", "Chakraborty", role = "aut"))
Description: Comprehensive clinical prediction equations for cardiopulmonary 
    exercise testing (CPET) and pulmonary function testing (PFT). Implements 
    FRIEND VO2 predictions (Silva et al. 2020), maximum heart rate (Arena et al. 
    2016), O2 pulse calculations (Ross et al. 2020), peak ventilation (Kaminsky 
    et al. 2018), and maximum voluntary ventilation (ATS 2003). Includes GLI 2021 
    Global (race-neutral) spirometry reference equations (Bowerman et al. 2023) 
    for FEV1, FVC, and FEV1/FVC ratio with predicted values, lower/upper limits 
    of normal, z-scores, and percent predicted calculations. Designed for use in 
    pulmonary function laboratories and exercise physiology clinics.
